<div class="home jumbotron">
  <h1>Welcome to <span class="home-title">Warlock Mind</span>, <%= current_user.first_name %></h1>

  <h2>This is one of many projects made by Kaemon Lovendahl! You can find other projects on my
    <a href="http://kaemon-lovendahl.surge.sh/", target="_blank">portfolio website</a>.</h2>

  <p>Warlock Mind is designed to make playing 5th edition much easier, so that you can spend less time:</p>
  <ul class="home__list">
    <li>Looking up rules</li>
    <li>Tracking Monster Stats</li>
    <li>Finding Equipment, Spells, and Adventuring gear.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>In order to focus on the game!</p>

  <hr />

  <p><em>
